Most of the text in the task is written in two languages, first english then czech.
Vetsina textu v tomto ukolu je napsana ve dvou jazycich, nejdrive anglicky, pak cesky.

---EN---

Hello, in this task will try little bit of what it is like to work as Red Hat tester and developer.
You will get to see simplified version of how our tests look like and how packaging works.
To complete this task you should know basics of working with Linux command line and a bit of programming (python),
but you don't need to worry, there will be hints on how to continue, if you get stuck.
Everything you will need to complete this task is contained in this directory level2/ later called
"level directory".
Now open file assignment.txt which will explain exactly what you need to do to comlete the task.

---CZ---

Zdravim, v tomto ukolu si budete moct castecne vyzkouset jake to je pracovat v Red Hatu jako tester a developer.
Uvidite zjednodusenou verzi toho jak vypadaji nase testy a jak funguje balickovani.
Pro dokonceni ukolu byste znat zaklady prace s Linuxovou prikazou radkou a trochu programovani (python),
ale nemusite se bat, pokud se na necem zaseknete, budete mit k dispozici rady jak pokracovat.
Vsechno co budete potrebovat pro uspesne dokonceni ukolu se nachazi v tomto adresari level2/,
ktery v dokumentaci nazyvame "levelovy adresar".
Nyni otevrete soubor assignment.txt ktery vam vysvetli co presne musite udelat abyste ukol dokoncili.
